# Testing & quality

- **Fix the root cause**: Don’t “paper over” failing tests by loosening assertions unless the requirement truly changed.
- **Unit tests**:
  - Prefer deterministic tests (no time/network/randomness without control).
  - For browser APIs (`localStorage`, `fullscreen`, `canvas`), use explicit mocks/stubs in tests.
- **Lint/style**:
  - Keep ESLint/Stylelint happy for edited files.
  - If formatting changes are needed, prefer running the formatter rather than manual whitespace edits.

